reviewText:
Gene Autry is an icon of cowboy, music, and Hollywood history.  Every baby boomer grew up with Gene Autry at some time in their tv viewing experience.
His music set the standard for classics.  He was a 'first'.  An empire.  The good guys always won back in the day!

6 Great Movies - Includes Boots & Saddles, Rim of The Canyon, Rancho Grande, Melody Ranch, The Big Show, Home of the Prairie  Total time = 342 min B/W - A super tape that consolidates some of the hits by the Singing Cowboy, Gene Autry!
